# Style Rewrite Pipeline — Detect Framework → Write New

## Pipeline Flow

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["Original Script"] --> B["1. Detect Framework"]
    B --> C["Original uses: e.g. Deep-Dive"]
    A --> D["2. Extract Blueprint"]
    D --> E["Blueprint JSON: facts, events, themes"]
    C --> F["3. Select Different Framework"]
    F --> G["Selected: e.g. Zoom Lens"]
    G --> H["4. Generate Outline"]
    E --> H
    H --> I["New Outline with new structure"]
    I --> J["5. Write Each Chapter"]
    E --> J
    J --> K["New Script — same content, different structure"]
```

